data.name: txthowtoplay.Text
data.value:
Game options: Shape - Type of shape E.g. Square, Circle Background Image - Image or gif used in the background. (Can be selected) Time to click - Amount of time before timer runs out and you lose Random colour - Changes colour of the shape when it is clicked Sound FX - Sound effects (mute or unmute) Shape size - Size of the shape. (In pixels) Shape colour - Colour of shape
Settings: Font style - Style of the font (Bold and regular) Audio / Volume - Select sound volume (0 - 100) Video - Select between windowed and fullscreen - Enable or disable double buffering
